122
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:33,610
Hraju si s tebou, protože ses nudila.

123
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:36,820
Uprchlého Izanagiho papadl vztek.

124
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:40,160
