170
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:31,120
Jo.

171
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:34,080
Páni.

172
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,920
Ah...

173
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,590
Úžasný, co?

174
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,640
