186
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:33,890
Znáš Shougo Hironoua?

187
00:13:34,060 --> 00:13:35,680
Neznám.

188
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,030
Bože.

189
00:13:47,070 --> 00:13:48,740
Neupravený?

190
