211
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:46,130
Skvělá odpověď, pane Hironou.

212
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:49,420
Co myslíte?

213
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:51,970
No...

214
00:14:53,010 --> 00:14:54,890
