215
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:58,260
No, jestli bys ráda...

216
00:14:58,390 --> 00:14:59,810
Ne, tak to není.

217
00:14:59,970 --> 00:15:01,310
Ovšem, že ne.

218
00:15:01,430 --> 00:15:02,980
Je to jen vtip.

219
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:04,980
Natsume...

220
00:15:05,150 --> 00:15:09,320
